OL,7,FA voyeur who recorded women in toilet
OL,8,Fcubicles for his own sexual
OL,9,Fgratification has been jailed.
OL,11,FPawanjit Singh, also known as Robbie,
OL,12,Fsnuck into female toilets and hid in
OL,13,Fcubicles before using his mobile phone
OL,14,Fto secretly record his victims as they
OL,15,Fused the toilet next to him.
OL,17,FHe captured 26 clips and six images of
OL,18,Fnumerous women in several different
OL,19,Fpubs in the North East in September
OL,20,F2020.
