OL,7,FIn May 2021, the 35-year-old was
OL,8,Fcaught by a woman as he was in the act
OL,9,Fof recording her in the female toilets
OL,10,Fat Washington Service Station. The
OL,11,Fwoman confronted him, and subsequently
OL,12,Fcontacted police.
OL,14,FThe investigation progressed when
OL,15,Fpolice accessed Singh's mobile phone
OL,16,Fand, after interrogating the device,
OL,17,Funcovered the voyeuristic content.
