OL,7,FSingh was charged with 27 offences of
OL,8,Fvoyeurism and appeared at South
OL,9,FTyneside Magistrates court in April
OL,10,Fwhere he pleaded guilty to all counts.
OL,12,FOn Thursday 2 May, Singh, of Henry
OL,13,FStreet, Shiney Row, appeared at
OL,14,FNewcastle Crown Court and was
OL,15,Fsentenced to one year in prison.
OL,17,FHe will spend 10 years on the Sex
OL,18,FOffenders' Register, was given a
OL,19,FSexual Harm Prevention Order (SHPO)
OL,20,Fand was ordered to have his devices
OL,21,Fdestroyed.
